    <div class="card-body">
      <p><b>Q. Set up a continuous integration system for your team's development work. Gilab CI CD is recommended.
          However, you may use any continuous integration solution you like as long as the essential features are
          implemented. You should have a regression test suite and at least a code coverage metric.</b></p>
